Zhao,"This will truly be one for the history books, General Iroh. Just think, centuries from now, people will study the great Admiral Zhao, who destroyed the last of the Water Tribe civilization. You're lucky you're here to see it.",这将真正成为历史书籍Iroh将军的一本。试想，几个世纪以后，人们将研究伟大的海军上将赵，他摧毁了最后的水族文明。你很幸运，你在这里看到它。
